                <li>Recreation equipment rental facilities</li>
                <li>Community event and festival spaces</li>
                <li>Tourism business support facilities</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Process Excellence -->
      <section class="process-section">
        <div class="container">
          <h2>Our Milford Concrete Coating Process</h2>
          
          <div class="process-steps">
            <div class="process-step">
              <div class="step-number">1</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h3>Environmental Assessment</h3>
                <p>
                  Comprehensive evaluation of your Milford property including moisture conditions, 
                  historic considerations, and Little Miami River valley environmental factors.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="process-step">
              <div class="step-number">2</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h3>Specialized Solution Design</h3>
                <p>
                  Custom coating system selection based on riverside conditions, historical requirements, 
                  and your specific needs within Milford's unique environment.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="process-step">
              <div class="step-number">3</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h3>Expert Installation</h3>
                <p>
                  Professional application using techniques adapted for riverside conditions and 
                  historic preservation requirements, with minimal community disruption.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="process-step">
              <div class="step-number">4</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h3>Performance Guarantee</h3>
                <p>
                  Thorough inspection and environmental performance testing to ensure your Milford 
                  installation meets our quality standards and environmental challenges.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Customer Testimonials -->
      <section class="testimonials">
        <div class="container">
          <h2>Milford Customer Experiences</h2>
          
          <div class="testimonials-grid">
            <div class="testimonial">
              <div class="testimonial-content">
                <p>
                  "Living near the Little Miami River, we always had moisture issues in our basement. 
                  The specialized coating system has completely solved the problem while creating 
                  beautiful space our family can actually use."
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="testimonial-author">
                <strong>Patricia & John M.</strong> - Riverside Milford Residents
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="testimonial">
              <div class="testimonial-content">
                <p>
                  "Our historic downtown business needed flooring that would respect the building's 
                  character while handling daily restaurant operations. They delivered exactly what 
                  we needed - beautiful, practical, and perfectly suited to our location."
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="testimonial-author">
                <strong>Restaurant Owner</strong> - Historic Main Street
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="testimonial">
              <div class="testimonial-content">
                <p>
                  "Our recreation facility serves thousands of bike trail visitors each season. 
                  The flooring has handled the constant traffic beautifully while maintaining 
                  an attractive appearance that represents Milford well."
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="testimonial-author">
